data.description: This charming brick condo is conveniently located within walking distance of bustling Uptown Centerville in Centerville Schools. The living room exudes peace and warmth, complete with a cozy gas fireplace.  The bright kitchen opens to the dining area and overlooks a private back patio. Ample cabinet & closet space on every level ensures easy organization and decluttering. The full finished basement provides additional storage and a versatile space to suit you. An attached one-car garage offers secure parking and extra storage. In the warmer months, the well-maintained community pool is ideal for lounging or a leisurely swim. Whether you prefer a leisurely stroll or a quick drive, everything you need is just moments away. Come experience the charm of 53 Wythe Parish & its maintenance free-living for yourself! No more leaf raking or snow shoveling! The sellers have loved this place for 20 years, and now they are offering 1% in closing costs to help the new owner make it their home.
